<body class="text-center">
  <form class="form-signin back" method="post" action="pay">
    <h1 class="title h3 mb-3 font-weight-normal">Paso 2: Módulo</h1>
    <p class="text">Por favor, selecciona el módulo a tomar.</p>
    <div class="mb-3">

      <div class="text-left options">
        <div class="form-check">
          <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="module" id="exampleRadios1" value="Basic"
            checked>
          <label class="form-check-label" for="exampleRadios1">
